definitions.definition: A small village in Kyloe parish, Northumberland , England ( OS grid ref NU0043 ) .
A small village and civil parish in Shropshire , England ( OS grid ref SJ5206 ) .
A small village in Tenbury parish, Malvern Hills district, Worcestershire , England ( OS grid ref SO5667 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
